---
title: Mediterranean Salmon with Creamy Dill Sauce, Green Beans & Za’atar Couscous
description: If you haven’t tried za’atar yet, well, then what za’atar you even doing? The Middle Eastern herb and spice blend has tart, nutty flavors that liven up pretty much anything—here, that’s couscous, which goes from plain to perfect. Not that this dish is otherwise lacking in flavor: Between the tender and flaky salmon, green beans, and creamy dill sauce, there’s plenty of impressive elements to choose from.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-salmon-0f503f3e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mediterranean-salmon-5ffc9664717f6e0f11468895-be2d3c03.pdf
